    Implement dual authentication system
    
    - Complete rewrite of auth.py to handle both REST API and Firebase authentication
    - Update api.py to use REST token for all API calls
    - Update ws.py to use Firebase token for WebSocket connection
    - Update config_flow.py to validate credentials using REST API
    - Update __init__.py to initialize dual authentication system
    - Add comprehensive error handling and token refresh logic
    - Support both authentication methods as required by Rointe system
    
    This resolves the authentication issues by implementing the correct
    dual authentication approach for Rointe's web + mobile app system.

